  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/ce2dc9b3c3af231ae8a6e07bd2f1891c.poster.avif?t=1751974146\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/ce2dc9b3c3af231ae8a6e07bd2f1891c.webm?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/ce2dc9b3c3af231ae8a6e07bd2f1891c.mp4?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The hero's journey of a pig who refuses to become a sausage!</strong></h2>There once was a peaceful farm, where lazy pigs lived behind a low fence.<br>Until, one day, they smashed the fence and made their great escape!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/cab2e4c5595f6a4fab23072d0ec23392.poster.avif?t=1751974146\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/cab2e4c5595f6a4fab23072d0ec23392.webm?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/cab2e4c5595f6a4fab23072d0ec23392.mp4?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pigs make the best sausages!</strong></h2>Pipes shooting fire, freezers, saw blades, conveyor belts! A variety of devices await the pigs.<br>Help our boy pig avoid becoming a sausage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/73dfce3bb2027a8ab9dbdf9ed12ec710.poster.avif?t=1751974146\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/73dfce3bb2027a8ab9dbdf9ed12ec710.webm?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/73dfce3bb2027a8ab9dbdf9ed12ec710.mp4?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging puzzles and tricky platforming!</strong></h2>Machines that recognize cutting lines, lift chases, and relentless butchers! Solve dangerous puzzles inside the sausage factory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/ac08d7ad98d1fc8bb64d94d38aaa4493.poster.avif?t=1751974146\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/ac08d7ad98d1fc8bb64d94d38aaa4493.webm?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362120/extras/ac08d7ad98d1fc8bb64d94d38aaa4493.mp4?t=1751974146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A grand orchestral soundtrack!</strong></h2>Escape the terrifying and brutal sausage factory to the tune of a grand orchestral soundtrack tailor-made for the story of Pig Romance!",
